  "contentFields": [
    {
      "contentFieldValue": {
        "data": "<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<div class=\"article-content\">\n<section class=\"article-body\">\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9SF6KY1EAQ17VRHQQAWX\">Added</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>​<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-40037\">LCD-40037</a> - Collapsible Lateral Menu:</strong> Added a new button to collapse the lateral menu, displaying only icons to conserve screen space. The menu's state will be remembered across screens, and tooltips will provide hints for collapsed sections.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"h_01HXYS9NRE5H6PTZ9Y99PF8QQH\">Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul class=\"ak-ul\">\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-40789\">LCD-40789</a> - Fixed Service Deletion Bug: </strong>Fixed an issue where the system would incorrectly interact with an ECK cluster, preventing services from being deleted. </li>\n<li>\n<strong><a href=\"https://liferay.atlassian.net/browse/LCD-40288\">LCD-40288</a> - Support For Larger Client Extension Config Files:</strong> Fixed an issue where larger client extension config files would fail to deploy by raising the limit to 1MB. We're exploring further optimizations to improve the user experience.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>"
      },
